political because he shot the man on national 
television. He was not political, but he was very

26:52.439 --> 27:04.476
well respected by the South Vietnamese because he 
was an airborne general and he came up the hard way

26:52.439 --> 27:04.476
and made no pretense of anything other than a 
combat infantryman. Now, at the time, he was in

27:04.496 --> 27:10.665
charge of the Saigon police because it was a 
military emergency. This innocent civilian,

27:12.670 --> 27:28.886
this guy in civilian clothes that got a bullet in 
the head, was a North Vietnamese Army lieutenant

27:12.670 --> 27:28.886
who had just led a unit that had just slaughtered 
the family of General Loan's aide. He had been

27:28.906 --> 27:29.627
caught. He was brought in. And they said, this is 
the one. And as General Loan said, I am a general

27:35.372 --> 27:40.197
officer authorized to conduct a summary court 
under emergency conditions, and I conducted it.

27:44.823 --> 27:50.671
And he shot the man, and that is why nobody has ever 
brought that man up on war crafts. Every military

27:51.111 --> 28:04.449
officer in the world knows that an enemy officer in 
civilian clothes who has just committed an

27:51.111 --> 28:04.449
atrocity, I'm not talking about blowing up a 
military installation. The man slaughtered a

28:04.469 --> 28:06.792
guy's family, for God's sakes.

28:09.438 --> 28:37.707
has the right to execute that individual whether 
the trial takes three days three years or three

28:09.438 --> 28:37.707
minutes is up to the convening officer and that's 
that general i'm sure that if it hadn't been his aid

