28:09.438 --> 28:37.707
quite probably have told him to take him over and 
use a firing squad But this was such an atrocity to

28:39.357 --> 28:44.242
this general that he personally took his pistol 
and killed the man. Kind of the spur of the moment.

28:46.405 --> 28:47.346
Not spur of the moment. I'm sure he was that angry. 
Oh, yeah. Yeah, it may have been spur of the moment,

