But when those kind of decisions are made, And they 
still commit Americans. Or we would effectively

42:23.880 --> 42:27.166
stop the enemy flow of supplies. Allow the 
interdiction. Stop the flow of supplies. And then

42:32.715 --> 42:34.818
the North would say, we'd like to talk. We'd stop 
